      "text": "5. Itt ka Karstums fafaltu-\nschâ Weetâ/ ta nospeedifi tu to\nSivefehineeku Warras-Darbu/\nta tas Karstums zaar to Pa-\nwehni weenas beezas Badebbes/\n(tâ) taps to Breesmigo Dseedaf-\nchana paſemnota.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Un tas KUNGS Zebaot\nDarrihs wiſſeem Laudim us fcho\nKalnu tankas Dſibres/ Dſibres\nno tchkiſta Wiha/ no Tau-\nfeim/ Smadsenceem/ un no Wiḫ-\nna/ kas no Meelehm nolaiftis irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Un wiſſch aprihs us fcho\nKalnu ta Waiga Apſegguar ko\nwiſſi Laudis apſegti irr/ un to\nApklahjumu/ar ko wiſſi Pagani\napflahti irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Wiſſch aprihs to Nahwi\nmuſchigi. Un tas Kungs\nKUNGS noſlauzibs tahs Akka-\nras no wiſſeem Waigeem / un\natxeins to Neewafchann ſawo\nLauschu no wiſſas Semmes\nWirfas/ jo tas KUNGS irr to\nrunnais.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Un tai Deena taps faſ-\nzihfs: Redſi/ tchis irr muhſu\nDeews/ mehs effam winnu ſa-\ngaidtifschi/ un wiſſch muhs iſpe-\nſihs. Schis irr tas KUNGS/\nmehs effam winnu ſagaidifschi/\nmehs preezaſimees un lihgimoſi-\nmees eekſch winnu Pefiſchanaas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Jo ta KUNGA Rohka\nduffehs us fcho Kalnu. Bet\nMoabs taps appalſch winna ſa-\nkults/ itt ka Salmi tohp famih-\nditi Subdoſ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Un wiſſch iſplattihſ ſa-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "was Rohkas winna Widdn/ it\nka weens Peſdetais tahs iſplat-\nta peſdedams/ un wiſſch paſein\nmoſs winna Grefnibu ar ſaw\nRohko Elkonieem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "12. Un wiſſch tohs augſtu-\nStiprumus taiwu Muhen loh-\nzihs/ paſemmoſs un mettihs toh\nPihſchloſ pee Semmes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XXVI. Nodalla.\nWena frahihna un jauka Leifſchanas Dsee-\nma tahs Draudses Kristus/ preekſch to bri-\nnign Uſturrefchannu prett wiſſeem Eenai-\nneekeem : 1.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "1. Ai Deena taps ſch\nDſecfina dſeedata eekſch\ntahs Semmes Juha-\nMuins irr weens ſtiprs Vilſ-\ntahts/ Wiſſch leek to Pefiſcha-\nnu par Muheem un Stipru-\nmeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "2. Atdarrajt tahs Wahrtis\nka ee-eet tee tafnii Laudis / ka\nto Peetizzibu ſarga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "3. Schi irr weena ſtipra Ap-\nnemſchana/ tu ſargi paſtahwig-\nMeeru/ jo us tewi tee paſaujahs\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "4. Patanjeetees us to KUN-\nGU muſchigt/ jo tis KUNG\nKUNGS irr weens Akminia-\nKalns muſchigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "5. Jo wiſſch nolohſa toh-\nangſus Eedſihwotaſus/ to pa-\nangſinatu Pilſfahtu: Wiſſch-\npaſemmo to/ wiſſch paſemmo t-\npee Semmes/ wiſſch mett t-\nPihſchloſ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "6. Ar Kahjahm winnu fa-\nmihſ/ to Behdigo Kahjas/ t-\nNabbago Pehdas.\n"
    }
  ],
